{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"987002af0a","title":"给宋庆龄的两封信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4b526df87d","index":0,"year":1949,"month":1,"day":19,"articleId":"987002af0a"},{"id":"57ccc047e8","index":1,"year":1949,"month":6,"day":19,"articleId":"987002af0a"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji5","name":"毛泽东文集第五卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/wenji5.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji5":{"comments":[{"id":"5f5aad17f4","publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"987002af0a","index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"根据手稿刊印。"},{"id":"3e76de75d4","publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"987002af0a","index":1,"part_index":3,"offset":124,"text":"梦醒，即廖梦醒（一九○四——一九八八），广东惠阳人。当时是宋庆龄的秘书。"},{"id":"c7cc3f8a84","publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"987002af0a","index":2,"part_index":3,"offset":130,"text":"汉年，即潘汉年，当时是中国共产党派往上海、香港开展统一战线工作的负责人。仲华，即金仲华（一九○七——一九六八），浙江桐乡人，当时在上海做统战工作。"},{"id":"34fb82548b","publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"987002af0a","index":3,"part_index":10,"offset":46,"text":"邓颖超，当时任中共中央候补委员、中华全国民主妇女联合会副主席。"}],"contents":[{"id":"c8398b20a6","type":"title","text":"给宋庆龄的两封信","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"987002af0a"},{"id":"3e76de75d4","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"987002af0a"},{"id":"c7cc3f8a84","type":"paragraph","text":"庆龄先生：","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"987002af0a"},{"id":"34fb82548b","type":"paragraph","text":"中国革命胜利的形势已使反动派濒临死亡的末日，沪上环境如何，至所系念。新的政治协商会议将在华北召开，中国人民革命历尽艰辛，中山先生遗志迄今始告实现，至祈先生命驾北来，参加此一人民历史伟大的事业，并对于如何建设新中国予以指导。至于如何由沪北上，已告梦醒与汉年、仲华切商，总期以安全为第一。谨电致意，伫盼回音。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"987002af0a"},{"id":"758ab3e6fa","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"987002af0a"},{"id":"d723cf2989","type":"paragraph","text":"周恩来","index":5,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"987002af0a"},{"id":"9dce31edd1","type":"paragraph","text":"子皓","index":6,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"987002af0a"},{"id":"5071ddc7cd","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":7,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"987002af0a"},{"id":"f25a57c7bb","type":"paragraph","text":"庆龄先生：","index":8,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"987002af0a"},{"id":"71fc68f3e4","type":"paragraph","text":"重庆违教，忽近四年。仰望之诚，与日俱积。兹者全国革命胜利在即，建设大计，亟待商筹，特派邓颖超同志趋前致候，专诚欢迎先生北上。敬希命驾莅平，以便就近请教，至祈勿却为盼！专此。敬颂大安！","index":9,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"987002af0a"},{"id":"7e64c37d85","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":10,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"987002af0a"},{"id":"374db7b0fe","type":"paragraph","text":"一九四九年六月十九日","index":11,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"987002af0a"}],"page":{"id":"a194532601","publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"987002af0a","start":250,"end":251}}}},"__N_SSG":true}